     <li>Bank Account Passbook.</li>
     <li>If the farm is your own, then the field’s Khasra number, account number.</li>
     <li>Proof of crop sowing.</li>
     <li>Photocopy of the agreement with the partner or owner if the field is in the field or on rent.</li>
     
     
